Lingua-ES-PhT version 0.9
==========================

Perl extension for phonetic/phonologic transcriptions in Spanish. Phonemes are
  represented with SAMPA symbols for Spanish, as defined at
  http://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/SAMPA_para_espa√±ol .

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Lingua::ES::Syllabify;
String::Multibyte;
TeX::Hyphen;

